name: A W(hole) lot of Holes
description:
Concept :

Dodge the Red holes in an infinite 3D runner with power ups (Green holes).

Programs/Websites used:

  • Game Engine : Unity 2019.3.0f6
  • 3D models : Blender 2.81
  • Icons : icons8.com
  • Sound Effects : sfxr

- Made for the Brackeys Game Jam 3, 2020
